AVAILABLE NOVEMBER 11! Spacious renovated 2 bedroom, 1 bath 997 square feet apartment home nestled in the heart of one of the most desirable areas of Salt Lake City, Sugarhouse.<br>
<br>
Your new home comes with energy-efficient appliances, updated cabinets, spacious patios/balconies*, vinyl plank flooring, access to a beautifully renovated courtyard, gas fireplaces*, and pet-friendly areas. All the more reason to fall in love with our community than ever before. Now is the perfect time to move in and start enjoying your enhanced lifestyle in an amazing neighborhood. *Available in select units.<br>
<br>
Our apartments in the Sugarhouse neighborhood of Salt Lake City offer easy access to one of Salt Lake’s most stunning neighborhoods. Here, you’re never far from eclectic shops, excellent eateries, and mountain views. With quick access to the TRAX S-Line stop, you’re minutes away from Downtown Salt Lake City when you reside at Ascent at Sugarhouse Cove. Westminster College and the beautiful Sugarhouse Park are within walking distance from this charming community. Come and see what this community has to offer you!<br>
<br>
Property Address: 2174 S. 300 E. South, South Salt Lake, UT 84115<br>
<br>
Rent: $1375<br>
<br>
For more information, take a virtual tour, schedule an in-person tour and to apply online, visit ascentsugarhousecove.com or call  <a href="#" class="show-contact" title="click to show contact info" data-href="/reply/slc/apa/7508467205/__SERVICE_ID__" rel="nofollow">show contact info</a>
  — or email us with your contact information and we'll have a community director reach out to you, at your convenience, with more information on floor plans, amenities, and to assist you with the application process.<br>
